queryResponse.sql:
SELECT
    last_delivery_market.latitude  AS "last_delivery_market.latitude",
    last_delivery_market.longitude  AS "last_delivery_market.longitude",
    CASE
WHEN accepted_bid.direction='inbound'  THEN '0'
WHEN accepted_bid.direction='outbound'  THEN '1'
WHEN nullif(accepted_bid.direction,'') is null  THEN '2'

END AS "accepted_bid.direction__sort_",
    CASE
WHEN accepted_bid.direction='inbound'  THEN 'Inbound'
WHEN accepted_bid.direction='outbound'  THEN 'Outbound'
WHEN nullif(accepted_bid.direction,'') is null  THEN 'Unknown'

END AS "accepted_bid.direction",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (case
        when shipments.is_tonu then null
        else shipments.carrier_rate
      end) <= (iff(shipments.is_tonu, null, shipment_carrier_manager_target_rate.amount))  THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipments_below_carrier_manager_target_count",
    AVG(( iff(shipments.is_tonu, null, shipments.carrier_rate)/nullif(shipments.calculated_miles,0)  ) ) AS "shipments.carrier_rpm_average"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipment_rates  AS shipment_carrier_manager_target ON shipment_carrier_manager_target.shipment_id=shipments.id and shipment_carrier_manager_target.rate_type_key='transfix_carrier_manager_target' and (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(shipment_carrier_manager_target.deprecated_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')) is null
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.rates  AS shipment_carrier_manager_target_rate ON shipment_carrier_manager_target_rate.id=shipment_carrier_manager_target.rate_id
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipment_stops  AS last_delivery ON last_delivery.shipment_id=shipments.id and last_delivery.last_stop and (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(last_delivery.deprecated_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')) is null
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.lk_kma  AS last_delivery_market ON (last_delivery_market.zip3=left(last_delivery.postal_code,3))
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.bids  AS accepted_bid ON shipments.id=accepted_bid.shipment_id
              and shipments.carrier_application_id=accepted_bid.carrier_application_id
              and (accepted_bid.accepted_by_id is not null and accepted_bid.carrier_application_id=shipments.carrier_application_id and (accepted_bid.declined_by_id is null))
              and (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(accepted_bid.declined_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) is null
WHERE ((( last_delivery.created_at  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( last_delivery.created_at  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', 6, DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))
GROUP BY
    1,
    2,
    3,
    4
ORDER BY
    5 DESC
FETCH NEXT 5000 ROWS ONLY

      end) <= (iff(shipments.is_tonu, null, shipment_carrier_manager_target_rate.amount))  THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipments_below_carrier_manager_target_count",
    AVG(( iff(shipments.is_tonu, null, shipments.carrier_rate)/nullif(shipments.calculated_miles,0)  ) ) AS "shipments.carrier_rpm_average"

LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipment_rates  AS shipment_carrier_manager_target ON shipment_carrier_manager_target.shipment_id=shipments.id and shipment_carrier_manager_target.rate_type_key='transfix_carrier_manager_target' and (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(shipment_carrier_manager_target.deprecated_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')) is null
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.rates  AS shipment_carrier_manager_target_rate ON shipment_carrier_manager_target_rate.id=shipment_carrier_manager_target.rate_id

              and (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(accepted_bid.declined_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) is null
WHERE ((( last_delivery.created_at  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( last_delivery.created_at  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('month', 6, DATEADD('month', -5, DATE_TRUNC('month', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))))
